  "operation_name": "aclnnAdaLayerNormQuant",
  "description": "接口功能：AdaLayerNormQuant算子将AdaLayerNorm和下游的量化（目前仅支持DynamicQuant）融合起来。该算子主要是用于执行自适应层归一化的量化操作，即将输入数据进行归一化处理，并将其量化为低精度整数，以提高计算效率和减少内存占用。\n\n计算公式：\n1. 先对输入x进行LayerNorm归一化处理：LayerNorm(x) = (x - E(x)) / sqrt(Var(x) + epsilon) * weightOptional + biasOptional。\n2. 再通过自适应参数scale和shift来调整归一化结果：y = LayerNorm(x) * (1 + scale) + shift。\n3. 若smoothScalesOptional不为空，则：y = y * smoothScalesOptional。\n4. 然后对y计算最大绝对值并除以127以计算需量化为INT8格式的量化因子：quantScale = row_max(abs(y)) / 127。\n5. 最后y除以量化因子再四舍五入得到量化输出：out = round(y / quantScale)。\n其中，E(x)表示输入的均值，Var(x)表示输入的方差，row_max代表每行求最大值。",
  "api_flow": "two-step",
  "inter_parameter_constraints": [
    {
      "type": "type_equality",
      "params": [
        "x",
        "scale"
      ],
      "expr": "scale.dtype == x.dtype",
      "description": "参数scale的数据类型必须与x一致。",
      "source": "x",
      "target": [
        "scale"
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "type_equality",
      "params": [
        "x",
        "shift"
      ],
      "expr": "shift.dtype == x.dtype",
      "description": "参数shift的数据类型必须与x一致。",
      "source": "x",
      "target": [
        "shift"
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "type_dependency",
      "params": [
        "x",
        "weightOptional"
      ],
      "expr": "(weightOptional is None) or (weightOptional.dtype == x.dtype)",
      "description": "如果提供weightOptional，其数据类型必须与x一致。",
      "source": "x",
      "target": [
        "weightOptional"
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "type_dependency",
      "params": [
        "x",
        "biasOptional"
      ],
      "expr": "(biasOptional is None) or (biasOptional.dtype == x.dtype)",
      "description": "如果提供biasOptional，其数据类型必须与x一致。",
